            "value": "<p>This simple iron staff is capped with a faceted, clear gem.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The gem at the top of the staff glows as a torch, shedding bright light in a 20-foot radius (and dim light to the next 20 feet) for 10 minutes.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.Effect: Staff of Illumination]</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Light]</li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Everlight]</li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Everlight], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Holy Light]</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed ranks of all listed spells.</p>"
